name: alloc::collections::btree::node::Handle::<collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Mut<'a>, K, V, collections::btree::node::marker::Leaf>, collections::btree::node::marker::KV>::remove
doc:
Removes the key-value pair pointed to by this handle and returns it, along with the edge
